            <h1>
              Scrum在智能工控中的探索应用
            </h1>
            <h2>
              Scrum in the exploration of intelligent industrial control applications
            </h2>
            <div id="ctl00_LeftContentPlaceHolder_periodical">
              <p id="fulltext" style="visibility:visible">
                <a href="/Service/File/view/Scrum在智能工控中的探索应用.aspx?ID=Periodical_wjsjxx201108059" class="seeft">
                </a>
